OL,6,FPolice Scotland have said they would
OL,7,Fnot be taking action over Harry Potter
OL,8,Fauthor JK Rowling's social media posts
OL,9,Fabout transgender issues. ITV News
OL,10,FScotland Reporter Louise Scott has more
