OL,3,CPolice Scotland will not investigate
OL,4,CJK Rowling over hate crime law row
OL,6,FIt comes after the Hate Crime and
OL,7,FPublic Order (Scotland) Act came into
OL,8,Feffect on Monday, consolidating
OL,9,Fexisting hate crime legislation with
OL,10,Fthe aim to give extra protection to
OL,11,Ftransgender people.
OL,13,FHowever, women have not been given
OL,14,Fprotection under the law, with the
OL,15,FScottish government instead promising
OL,16,Fto bring forward legislation to tackle
OL,17,Fmisogyny.
