OL,3,CPolice Scotland will not investigate
OL,4,CJK Rowling over hate crime law row
OL,6,FThe Harry Potter author, who has
OL,7,Fbecome a fierce critic of the Scottish
OL,8,Fgovernment's stance on transgender
OL,9,Frights, has been one of the highest
OL,10,Fprofile challengers of the
OL,11,Flegislation, which she claims is "wide
OL,12,Fopen to abuse".
OL,14,FRowling, who does not believe people
OL,15,Fcan change their gender, insisted:
OL,16,F"Freedom of speech and belief are at
OL,17,Fan end in Scotland if the accurate
OL,18,Fdescription of biological sex is
OL,19,Fdeemed criminal."
