OL,3,CPolice Scotland will not investigate
OL,4,CJK Rowling over hate crime law row
OL,6,FAfter police confirmed they would not
OL,7,Finvestigate, Rowling wrote on X,
OL,8,Fformerly known as Twitter: "I hope
OL,9,Fevery woman in Scotland who wishes to
OL,10,Fspeak up for the reality and
OL,11,Fimportance of biological sex will be
OL,12,Freassured by this announcement, and I
OL,13,Ftrust that all women - irrespective of
OL,14,Fprofile or financial means - will be
OL,15,Ftreated equally under the law."
