OL,6,FShe also thanked supporters who had
OL,7,Fbacked her stance on the subject, and
OL,8,Fvowed to stand up for other women who
OL,9,Fwere prosecuted, adding: "If they go
OL,10,Fafter any woman for simply calling a
OL,11,Fman a man, I'll repeat that woman's
OL,12,Fwords and they can charge us both at
OL,13,Fonce."
OL,15,FRowling wrote to one user: "I won't
OL,16,Fever forget the support I've had x."
