OL,6,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak earlier
OL,7,Fsaid "nobody should be criminalised
OL,8,Ffor saying common sense things about
OL,9,Fbiological sex" after Rowling
OL,10,Fchallenged the Scottish government's
OL,11,Fnew legislation.
OL,13,FThe prime minister appeared to back
OL,14,Fthe author's criticism and said there
OL,15,Fare no plans "to do anything like that
OL,16,Fhere in England".
