OL,6,FIn a social media post, Rowling
OL,7,Fargued: "It is impossible to
OL,8,Faccurately describe or tackle the
OL,9,Freality of violence and sexual
OL,10,Fviolence committed against women and
OL,11,Fgirls, or address the current assault
OL,12,Fon women's and girls' rights, unless
OL,13,Fwe are allowed to call a man a man."
OL,15,FCriticising the new laws, she insisted
OL,16,Fthat the "legislation is wide open to
OL,17,Fabuse by activists who wish to silence
OL,18,Fthose of us speaking out about the
OL,19,Fdangers of eliminating women's and
OL,20,Fgirls' single-sex spaces".
