OL,6,FThe Act has also raised the ire of
OL,7,Fpolicing bodies, with the Scottish
OL,8,FPolice Federation (SPF) claiming
OL,9,Ftraining for officers is not enough
OL,10,Fand the Association of Scottish Police
OL,11,FSuperintendents (ASPS) raising
OL,12,Fconcerns about the legislation being
OL,13,Fweaponised for political purposes.
OL,15,FASPS warned vexatious complaints could
OL,16,Fbe made against people based on their
OL,17,Fviews by political opponents.
