OL,7,Fthere is "disinformation" being spread
OL,8,Fabout the Bill and what it entails,
OL,9,Fclaiming there is a "triple lock" of
OL,10,Fprotection for speech.
OL,12,FThis includes an explicit clause, a
OL,13,Fdefence for the accused's behaviour
OL,14,Fbeing "reasonable" and that the Act is
OL,15,Fcompatible with the European
