OL,6,FMr Yousaf also told journalists on
OL,7,FFriday that the legislation would not
OL,8,Fgo the way of other high-profile
OL,9,Flegislative U-turns under the SNP,
OL,10,Fsuch as the named persons scheme and
OL,11,Fthe Offensive Behaviour at Football
OL,12,FAct.
OL,14,FThe legislation, which he shepherded
OL,15,Fthrough Holyrood as former first
OL,16,Fminister Nicola Sturgeon's justice
OL,17,Fsecretary, "got the right balance"
OL,18,Fbetween protections against hate crime
OL,19,Fand freedom of speech, he said.
